\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri-570\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22 >Woe du gode dancken salst van sijnre opuerstandenysse ende hemelvaert.< {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5650[0].5666v/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22\chcbpat17 >O< alre suetste here, een liefhebber der ewiger salicheit, ic arm sunder benedije ende laue dy, mynen here}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs22  [57r] \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs22 ende mijnen got, wanttu mensche geworden bust om mynen wil ...
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri-570\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs20 Auch in{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5007[0].501m/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs20\chcbpat17  Darmstadt, ULB, Hs 992, Bl. 247v}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs20  (\plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs20 Achten/Knaus\plain \f1\lang1033\fs20 , S. 83, Nr. 20).}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg0\uc1\deff0\deflang0\deflangfe0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset1 Arial;}{\f1\fnil\fcharset0 Arial;}{\f2\fnil\fcharset0 Calibri;}}{\colortbl;\red0\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;\red0\green255\blue255;\red0\green255\blue0;\red255\green0\blue255;\red255\green0\blue0;\red255\green255\blue0;\red255\green255\blue255;\red0\green0\blue128;\red0\green128\blue128;\red0\green128\blue0;\red128\green0\blue128;\red128\green0\blue0;\red128\green128\blue0;\red128\green128\blue128;\red192\green192\blue192;\red204\green238\blue221;}

